"title": "5523: servants, good",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5523",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture identifies certain qualities which are found in good servants and requires that these qualities should be found in believers' service of God.</p>\n<h2>Qualities found in good servants</h2>\n<h3>Diligence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:10\">ECC 9:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:28\">1KI 11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:4\">PRO 10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:29\">PRO 22:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:14-Matt25:23\">MAT 25:14–25:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:12-Luke19:19\">LUK 19:12–19:19</a></p>\n<h3>Faithfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:2\">1CO 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:5-Exod21:6\">EXO 21:5–21:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:21\">2SA 15:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:11-2Chr34:12\">2CH 34:11–34:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:13\">NEH 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:13\">PRO 25:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:4\">DAN 6:4</a></p>\n<h3>Honesty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:7\">2KI 22:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:6\">GEN 39:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:15\">2KI 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:9-Titus2:10\">TIT 2:9–2:10</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:5\">EPH 6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:10\">LUK 17:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:22\">COL 3:22</a></p>\n<h3>Perseverance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:40-Gen31:41\">GEN 31:40–31:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:12-2Thess3:13\">2TH 3:12–3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Respect</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:1-1Tim6:2\">1TI 6:1–6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6\">MAL 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:18\">1PE 2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Willingness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:6-Eph6:7\">EPH 6:6–6:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:21\">1CH 28:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:9\">TIT 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of good servants</h2>\n<p>Abraham's servant:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:9\">GEN 24:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:49\">GEN 24:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:18\">2SA 12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:13-2Sam23:17\">2SA 23:13–23:17</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:13\">2KI 5:13</a> <em>Naaman's servants</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:9\">MAT 8:9</a> <em>a centurion's servants</em></p>\n<h2>Good servants are often rewarded by their employers</h2>\n<h3>They are advanced by them</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:4-Gen39:5\">GEN 39:4–39:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:18\">PRO 27:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:21\">MAT 25:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:23\">MAT 25:23</a></p>\n<h3>They have their confidence</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:2-Gen24:4\">GEN 24:2–24:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:10\">GEN 24:10</a></p>\n<h2>Good servants often bring blessings on their employers</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:27-Gen30:30\">GEN 30:27–30:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:2-Gen39:4\">GEN 39:2–39:4</a></p>\n<h2>Good servants have God with them</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:7\">GEN 24:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:27\">GEN 24:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:7\">GEN 31:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:42\">GEN 31:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:3\">GEN 39:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:21\">GEN 39:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:46\">MAT 24:46</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:9-Acts7:10\">ACT 7:9–7:10</a></p>",
